Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=Reality=The One and the Many
By: Maimonides
---
Foundation of foundations and firmest pillar of all wisdom is to know that
there is a First Being, that He caused all beings to be and that all beings
from heaven and earth and from between them could not be saved but for the
truth of His own being.
